{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2762 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2762 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C2762","pos":[597,617]},{"content":"'class' : invalid expression as a template argument for 'argument'","pos":[618,684]},{"pos":[691,824],"content":"When using <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>/Za<ept id=\"p1\">](../../build/reference/za-ze-disable-language-extensions.md)</ept>, the compiler will not convert an integral to a pointer.","source":"When using [/Za](../../build/reference/za-ze-disable-language-extensions.md), the compiler will not convert an integral to a pointer."},{"content":"The following sample generates C2762:","pos":[831,868]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2762 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2762\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2762\"\nms.assetid: 8b81a801-fd48-40a1-8bee-0748795b12e4\ncaps.latest.revision: 8\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2762\n'class' : invalid expression as a template argument for 'argument'  \n  \n When using [/Za](../../build/reference/za-ze-disable-language-extensions.md), the compiler will not convert an integral to a pointer.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2762:  \n  \n```  \n// C2762.cpp  \n// compile with: /Za  \ntemplate<typename T, T *pT>  \nclass X2 {};  \n  \nvoid f2() {  \n   X2<int, 0> x21;   // C2762  \n   // try the following line instead  \n   // X2<int, static_cast<int *>(0)> x22;  \n}  \n```"}